HOW TO GET CHANGES FROM PRODUCTION
----------------------------------

1. cp load_balancer.conf from dokimion.psont:/etc/nginx/sites-available/load_balancer.conf

2. change testing.languagetechnology to test_staging.languagetechnology

3. change prod_server to stage_server

